ComicInfo.Series: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero
ComicInfo.Summary: Darklon returns to Darklonia, then sets off to Benzheen in his quest to obtain the Krytron. Clutch and Rock & Roll survey Cobra's actions as they move into their new base. A G.I. Joe already on the ground in Benzheen is startled to see Darklon arrive.
